---
title: Super Speedy Indian Halloumi Curry & Rice with Veggies & Coriander
description: Spice up dinner-time with this North Indian curry! Golden, pan-fried halloumi takes center stage in a rich, aromatic curry packed with veggies and bold flavours. Served with fluffy rice and a sprinkle of fresh coriander, it’s a hearty, vibrant dish that’s perfect for curry night. Say hello to your new favourite comfort food!
